<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idc30f2e53-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1973-09-01">Sept. 1, 1973</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/93/82/s501">section 501 of Pub. L. 93–82</ref>, set out as an Effective Date of 1973 Amendment note under <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s1701">section 1701 of this title</ref>.</p>
